data.actual_result: The server appears in the list. Also, when clicking on the server it brings you to a blank screen with a "No Text Channels" message.
data.expected_result: The server should not appear in the list.
data.short_description: Able to go to non-existent server in "Find or start a conversation"
data.steps_to_repro: - Open "Find or start a conversation" - Locate a server in the list. - Delete that server from another device - Click on that server which is now at the end of the list.
